---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '../data/site-config.ts';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Casa dos Duques — A 90-Year-Old Renovated Holiday Home in Abiul, Pombal"
  description="Discover the story of Casa dos Duques: a meticulously renovated 90-year-old house with original stones, terracotta floors, high ceilings, and a warm family ambience in Abiul, Pombal."
  canonical="/the-house/"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6">Casa dos Duques — A 90-Year-Old Renovated Holiday Home in Abiul</h1>
    
    <img src="/images/airbnb/d5facc44-501a-445c-8eb4-94cf90e682dc.jpeg" alt="Casa dos Duques exterior" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 h-96 object-cover" loading="eager" />

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mb-4">The Story of the House</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-warm leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Casa dos Duques has stood in the heart of Abiul for over 90 years. Built in a time when 
        craftsmanship was paramount, the house has witnessed the quiet rhythm of life in this 
        historic town — from its 1167 royal charter to the present day.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-warm leading-relaxed mb-4">
        After years of careful planning, the house was meticulously renovated with deep respect 
        for its original character. Every decision was made to preserve what makes it special: 
        the thick stone walls that keep the house cool in summer, the high ceilings that lend an 
        airy feel, the original terracotta floor tiles, and the exposed wooden structure that 
        tells the story of traditional Portuguese construction.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-warm leading-relaxed">
        The result is a holiday home that feels both timeless and comfortable — a warm, inviting 
        space where friends and family can gather, relax, and create memories.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mb-4">Living Spaces</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-warm-cream rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-olive-800 mb-2">🛋️ Living Room</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-warm text-sm leading-relaxed">A cozy living room with a fireplace, perfect for cooler evenings. Comfortable seating, warm lighting, and a relaxed atmosphere.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-warm-cream rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-olive-800 mb-2">🍳 Kitchen & Dining</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-warm text-sm leading-relaxed">Fully equipped kitchen with oven, fridge, Nespresso machine, kettle, microwave, and all utensils. Dining area for shared meals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mb-4">Restoration Details</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-warm">
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta-500">✦</span> High ceilings preserved throughout the house</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta-500">✦</span> Original stone walls carefully restored</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta-500">✦</span> Traditional red terracotta floor tiles maintained</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta-500">✦</span> Exposed wooden ceiling structure kept as a feature</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta-500">✦</span> Thick walls provide natural insulation — cool in summer, warm in winter</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

  <CTASection
    title="Experience Casa dos Duques"
    subtitle="Book your stay and discover the charm of this beautifully restored holiday home"
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Check Availability', href: '/booking/' }}
    secondaryCta={{ label: 'See the Rooms', href: '/rooms/' }}
    variant="olive"
  />
</BaseLayout>
